	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I think for the SNES and GBC it's different, but the NES's attribute table only keeps track of color information. So yeah, the answer is sadly no. You'll have to think a bit outside the box if you want to display reversed graphics.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


