	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Interesting, I guess the GBC also have the ability to flip BG tiles and have background priority which is an extra to what the NES can do.
<br />
<br />Note that if you have CHR-RAM it's always possible to flip tiles in software. I know it still wastes VRAM, but at least it doesn't waste ROM.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


